User Story 1
  As an average user, I want to singup, so that I can have a profile where all of my questions and answers are saved.

User Story 2
  As an average user, I want to change my password, so that I can change it if my account gets hacked or my account is vunlerable.

User Story 3
  As an average user, I want to be able to mark images as NSFW, so that other average users dont have to look at the image if they dont want to.

User Story 4
